name: checkingLineReferencePlaceHolder

testSteps.description: Given that I'm logged in to Voucher Entry page

children.description: When i open page from sidebar menu: {Accounts Payable,Voucher Entries,Voucher Entry}

testSteps.description: Then the Payment Information form and its contents should show up
When I set the Supplier to '133339'
When I set the 'Invoice Number' to 'sJOhLDUnbz'
When I set the Currency to 'USD'
When i click on continue button
When I select the first Bank Account and click 'Submit' button if modal exist
When I set the Gross Amount to '15000'
When I set the Payment Terms to '30'
When I set the Tax Area to 'KF7'
When i click on continue button
Then the 'GL Distribution' form and its contents should show up
When I fill up the last row line using Account Number: '580000', Line Description: 'Test', Amount: '1', Cost Center: '1MAN400', Gen Obj: '<null>', AOE: 'YAO', Line Ref: 'Test1'
When I click on the 'Show Next' button
When i clear the line ref field of last line
Then the line ref placeholder of the last line should be: YYMMXXXNN
When I set the 'AOE' to 'Test1'
When I click on 'Show Previous' button
When I click 'Add Line' button
When I fill up the last row line and balance the amount using Account Number: '390000', Line Description: 'Test', Cost Center: '1MAN400', Gen Obj: '<null>', AOE: 'YAO', Line Ref: 'Test1'
When I click on the 'Show Next' button
When i clear the line ref field of last line
Then the line ref placeholder of the last line should be: GXXXNNN
When I set the 'AOE' to 'Test1'
When I click on 'Save' button
Then the voucher entry successfully created modal and its contents should show up

title: Checking line reference place holder
